00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:01,480
It's the only place where real hope will be.

480
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:07,500
And we need to be people of hope, sharing that hope in a world that is frantic

481
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:13,810
for some kind of rooting, for some kind of vine to be attached to.

482
00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:18,700
And I want them to see it in the people of Fullerton first.

483
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:22,280
I mean, I want all the church in America, but I can't speak to all that.

484
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:24,680
All I know is we got us right here.

485
00:35:25,830 --> 00:35:27,150
And can we encourage each other?

486
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:33,240
Can I encourage you and can you encourage me to be the most fruitful kind of disciples that we can be?

487
00:35:33,240 --> 00:35:39,320
To use our spiritual gifts to the fullest, to prune away the leaves and the brush that holds us back

488
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:45,990
from having beautiful, luscious fruit that makes the Father proud and glorifies Him.

489
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:47,640
I'm going to pray.

490
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:50,660
I'm going to pray that God's Spirit is going to move in this place.

491
00:35:51,220 --> 00:35:53,660
I'm going to invite you up to prayer if you'd like to come.

492
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,720
I'm going to invite you to get things right with God.

493
00:35:55,800 --> 00:36:00,740
I'm going to invite you to have an encounter with Jesus for the first time if you've never done that.

494
00:36:01,990 --> 00:36:06,960
Because I want you to be fruitful, beautiful, luscious, fruitful disciples.

495
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:09,960
And so with that, let's pray.

496
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:18,650
Lord God, thank you for Jesus' strong words as he shares with his intimate disciples.

497
00:36:18,650 --> 00:36:23,230
and that's us carrying on the mission 2,000 years later.

498
00:36:24,620 --> 00:36:26,260
I pray we'd be faithful in that.

499
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:31,460
I pray that we would be fruitful as you called us to be fruitful.

500
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:36,340
And Lord, if there's some of us here that just are struggling

501
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:43,560
with the flow of your life into their lives,

502
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:46,060
there's things that block the flow, I pray.

503
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:51,140
Your spirit would now begin to prune and clip and part the brush.

504
00:36:53,790 --> 00:36:55,490
And may the flow grow.

505
00:36:55,490 --> 00:37:00,840
and may the blossoms begin to open.

506
00:37:04,130 --> 00:37:06,310
Father, we want to be people that are fruitful.

507
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,380
Help us to allow you to do your work

508
00:37:10,380 --> 00:37:11,840
and not resist it.

509
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,240
Help us to be a loving community

510
00:37:16,240 --> 00:37:18,200
that encourages each other towards

511
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:20,690
faithfulness and fruitfulness.

512
00:37:24,290 --> 00:37:25,250
So Lord, may it be so.

513
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:29,460
And this morning I want to speak for a moment

514
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:31,500
while our heads are bowed to anyone here

515
00:37:31,500 --> 00:37:36,740
that has not yet decided to lay aside the old life

516
00:37:36,740 --> 00:37:44,160
and to come and to have Jesus grab you onto his vine

517
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:50,200
and pour his life into yours and make it wonderful.

518
00:37:53,410 --> 00:37:57,270
If you're in that place and you're feeling the Holy Spirit's touch in your life right now,

519
00:37:57,330 --> 00:37:58,750
you might pray just like this.

520
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:03,210
Dear God, I know that you're there.

521
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:07,980
And I know that you see my life and where I've been.

522
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:10,620
And I'm sorry for where I've been, the things I've done

523
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:14,810
that go against the kind of life you would have for me.

524
00:38:14,810 --> 00:38:18,200
but I thank you that you forgive me

525
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:21,000
that you clear that all

526
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:23,920
away, that you prune

527
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:25,840
all those dead

528
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:27,200
and dying branches away

529
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:30,910
that you produce new life

530
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:32,430
thank you that

531
00:38:32,430 --> 00:38:34,620
I'm forgiven

532
00:38:34,620 --> 00:38:37,880
that I now have you in me

533
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:40,870
and I want to follow you all the days of my

534
00:38:40,870 --> 00:38:44,260
life and as the Bible says

535
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:47,060
I want to dwell in

536
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:48,100
your house forever

537
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:51,410
Lord may you do that work now

538
00:38:51,410 --> 00:38:54,300
and bring that kind of assurance now

539
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:57,950
in the lives of those who are giving their lives to you.

540
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:03,670
Father, I pray that in these days of uncertainty,

541
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:06,880
in these days of challenge around our globe,

542
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:10,100
I pray that you would unite the church,

543
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:13,780
that the church would be a beacon of hope,

544
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:16,970
and that though our emotions may jitter

545
00:39:16,970 --> 00:39:19,530
and our stomachs may rumble and we may be insecure,

546
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:22,530
Lord, may we be secure in you,

547
00:39:22,530 --> 00:39:25,450
the architect of the ages,

548
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:27,230
the God of all mercy,

549
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:30,410
the one who's sovereign over everything.

550
00:39:33,380 --> 00:39:34,480
May we trust in you.

551
00:39:35,530 --> 00:39:36,790
And may that be our comfort.

552
00:39:38,250 --> 00:39:41,950
And may the hugs and the handshakes of the disciples

553
00:39:41,950 --> 00:39:44,900
as we in Christ gather together,

554
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:48,320
may that be our comfort, our refuge,

555
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:52,180
our place of encouragement.

556
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:56,480
Lord God, accomplish your purposes.

557
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:59,820
And I pray you continue to raise up Fullerton First

558
00:39:59,820 --> 00:40:01,700
for the great fruit you want to produce.

559
00:40:02,100 --> 00:40:08,540
On this street corner, in this community, in North Orange County, at this time in the history of the world.

560
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:12,940
We want to be all about what you want us to be about.

561
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,920
So help us to see where you're taking us.

562
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:18,560
And may we follow.

563
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:22,920
And may we be fruitful along the way.

564
00:40:23,900 --> 00:40:26,550
In Jesus' name, amen.

